text: I just finished up our first batch of articles. I really like how we all have our own distinct styles to writing and our personality comes out. Nice job guys, I'm super proud to be involved with this.
I have had a few dozen people hit me up about wanting to contribute in the last 24 hours, as expected
We'll be adding some new people pretty soon
I noticed that too. I guess we had a pretty decent impact to start

The people who want to write once a month or not at all will gradually drop off and some people might go weekly, but I doubt it. Most likely we'll all do two a month. I may even write myself, I'm not sure yet. I have heard some very good pitches
Right on
It took a while to get enough content to launch which I anticipated but we'll have enough people interested that we'll have quality content moving forward. This is going just like we planned
